settings.description: Even if this editor seems kinda robust, it's kinda fun trying to build levels under the GBA's limitation. Level's mostly focused on the Triangular Block's mechanics.

name: To Bop or Not to Bop

settings.description: B.O.P = Bouncing On Pinheads (though Wigglers have very round heads) - Prod. Code: 084A, Rel: 9/1/22, 6:00pm, Accidental Rel: 6/?/22
Jump across spikes and lava, and make you way to the goal!
Hurry up, and reach the goal before time runs out!
Well, the objective is stupidly simple. Find the right level and don't do all that hard work for nothing! P-Wing included for special time wasting! Careful as something may block your path.
